    rootdev (Closes: #600453)
  * [f3b696b] Small enhancements to Maintainer docs.

  [ Marc Herbert ]
  * [478ba89] Minor documentation fix in /etc/initramfs-tools/modules.
    (LP: #177263)

 -- maximilian attems <maks@debian.org>  Thu, 21 Oct 2010 13:53:17 +0200

