    Thanks to Axel Beckert <beckert@phys.ethz.ch> for report.
  * hook-functions: MODULES=dep fix error message.

  [ Glennie Vignarajah ]
  * initramfs-tools: Fix UUID rootfs detection with 'MODULES=dep'.
    (closes: #483082)

